<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA2">
<l>iṭarkaḷaiyā rēṉu memakkiraṅkā rēṉum</l>
<l>paṭaru neṟipaṇiyā rēṉuñ - cuṭaruruvi</l>
<l>leṉpaṟāk kōlat teriyāṭu memmāṉārk</l>
<l>kaṉpaṟā teṉṉeñ cavarkku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
Even though he does not remove [our] misery, even though he does not feel pity for us, 
even though he does not ordain the path we set out on, our father 
with a glowing form, with beauty excelling in bones, who dances with a flame,
my heart never ceases in love to him.
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
